OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Hands off Africa' Pope    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsays on visit to DR Congo  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Shortly after landing in Kinshasa in   
OL,6, the Democratic Republic of the Congo,  
OL,7, Pope Francis delivered a speech full of
OL,8, stinging condemnation of the           
OL,9, exploitation over centuries - not just 
OL,10, of this country, but also the          
OL,11, continent.                             
OL,13,FHe talked of political strangleholds   
OL,14,Fgiving way to "economic colonialism",  
OL,15,Fwhich he said was equally enslaving.   
OL,17,FIn the best-received section of the    
OL,18,Fspeech he told the outside world to    
OL,19,Facknowledge the catastrophic things    
OL,20,Fthat have been done in the country and 
OL,21,Fto fully respect people here.          
